:::Wheeljack:::

Wheeljack: As you know, the Maximals have a new base, a city.  This project 
was started awhile ago by Zardus, and is very similar to the mission that the 
late Feline and Skulletron undertook when the Maximals had just settled into 
the Cybertronian Fire.  But this time i have equipped Vamprah and Composer 
with devices that mask energy signatures, fooling the Maximals into thinking 
they are one of them.  Vamprah has even been given a temporary new body 
design for this mission.  We were ready to go, but there is a battle going on 
a Maximal City right now.  We need your approval as to if we should go anyway 
or not.

--part1_26.1d09f57e.290440d4_boundary
